snippet.title: Best VGM 586 - Shadow of the Colossus - The Opened Way ~ Battle With the Colossus
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 422 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7lHAHFl_3u0

Best VGM 2404 - https://youtu.be/UhVWxNU6yag

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Shadow of the Colossus (2005)
The Opened Way ~ Battle With the Colossus
Koh Otani
